  <h2>Glass vs Plastic Meal Prep Containers</h2>
  <p>Choosing between glass and plastic is the biggest decision you'll make when buying meal prep containers. Both have distinct advantages depending on your lifestyle, commute, and cooking habits.</p>

  <div class="glass-plastic-grid">
    <div class="gp-box">
      <h3>Glass Containers</h3>
